            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " classes encapsulate and manage font families, sizes, and variations. The "
            },
            {
              "type": "reference",
              "isActive": false,
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/appkit/nsfont"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": " class defines a single object for each distinct font; for efficiency, these objects, which can be rather large, are shared by all the objects in your app. The "
